Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:47.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:49.16,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}忘れないで
