Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:49.16,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\fsp-1}不要遗忘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:54.18,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\fsp-1}我一直都在等待着你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.39,0:22:04.45,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\fsp-1}这淡淡香甜的日常 看似脆弱不堪
